{"tid":1666748,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] 水警車內燒炭亡 死因無可疑 [知道得太多?]","createTime":"2019-10-21T06:18:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T06:26:23.000Z","uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"26f43adda651c44765aff3928954e6883f2ffa9b","tid":1666748,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T06:18:23.000Z","msg":"#又係 on.c.c <br />\n#留意<span style=\"color: red;\">紅字</span>時間<br />\n<br />\n10月21日(一)<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">10:16建立</span><br />\n<br />\n救護員接報到場。(讀者提供)<br />\n<br />\n新田新潭路33號一地盤，<span style=\"color: red;\">今晨(21日)9時16分，警方接報</span>指在上址發現一名男子在私家車內昏迷，救援人員趕至現場，將事主救出，惟經檢驗後證實他已氣絕身亡。人員其後在車內發現一盆燒過的炭，懷疑事主燒炭自殺。警方封鎖現場調查事件原因。<br />\n<br />\n消息指，<span style=\"color: red;\">事主生前為一名水警警長，駐守水警北分區</span>，於前日(19日)疑與妻子因提早退休問題意見不合，發生口角，事主其後駕駛私家車離家。其妻見他徹夜未回，於昨日(20日)前往落馬洲警署報案。人員隨即四處尋找，惟至昨日下午，事主亦未有現身上班，惜至今晨始揭悲劇發生。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191021/bkn-20191021101613205-1021_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20191021%2Fbkn-20191021101613205-1021_00822_001.html&d=IZFSAkWTwbXSesVVmoeERR68f20TVEdZexmFDfnZHo4%3D&h=87aaad6d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191021/bkn-20191021101613205-1021_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"8073a0868e57ee723e76d6f741c89c96b12a108f","tid":1666748,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T06:18:40.000Z","msg":"[突發]今晚18區都有野搞<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1666302\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1666302</a>"},{"pid":"c3e5c7a984ddad53a6f602eff93bd374e76ff519","tid":1666748,"uid":321732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T06:26:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唉，業障重，黑驚幾時俾天收"}]}